00:32:39,680 --> 00:32:41,800
Yes, Your Highness.

280
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:52,780
Father, please let me continue reading.

281
00:32:52,780 --> 00:32:55,180
I said you can't!

282
00:32:55,180 --> 00:32:59,500
I will never get in the way of the Crown Prince.

283
00:32:59,500 --> 00:33:02,220
I don't even have the slightest motive.

284
00:33:02,220 --> 00:33:06,260
The books that the crown prince would take six years to read,

285
00:33:06,260 --> 00:33:11,040
you finished them all in 2 months. Isn't that eyeing the path of the crown prince?

286
00:33:11,040 --> 00:33:18,720
But, Father! How can I live without doing anything?

287
00:33:18,720 --> 00:33:19,820
What?

