00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:02,840
As always, you probably still don't like to serve me.

309
00:35:07,120 --> 00:35:12,920
That's why I want to introduce you to someone.

310
00:35:12,920 --> 00:35:14,620
Introduce?

311
00:35:14,620 --> 00:35:16,600
Come in.

312
00:35:25,100 --> 00:35:29,240
He's my third son, Lee Do.

313
00:35:33,460 --> 00:35:34,800
Your Highness.

314
00:35:34,800 --> 00:35:37,800
He is a very peculiar one.

315
00:35:41,080 --> 00:35:43,220
Peculiar?

316
00:35:43,220 --> 00:35:48,220
He's not like me. He's like the people I miss.

317
00:35:50,320 --> 00:35:55,200
He's the best warrior in Joseon, capable of facing 100 warriors by himself.

318
00:35:55,200 --> 00:35:57,400
Yes, Father.

319
00:35:58,900 --> 00:36:02,720
I don't know about other things but being calm and genuine,

320
00:36:02,720 --> 00:36:08,100
at least I don't think you'll make fun of me.

321
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:14,400
Don't you want to see her?

322
00:36:16,960 --> 00:36:20,880
I know which island she's on.

323
00:36:24,500 --> 00:36:26,660
Do you want to go?

324
00:36:45,380 --> 00:36:48,400
 Moohaengdo 

325
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:50,700
Starting this spring, instead of beans,

326
00:36:50,700 --> 00:36:53,280
I'm thinking of planting barley.

327
00:36:54,640 --> 00:37:00,280
Yes. Since we planted beans for three years on the cultivated land, the soil is probably better now.

328
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:01,640
I also think that way.

