337
00:38:05,640 --> 00:38:08,560
His Highness must be really happy.

338
00:38:08,560 --> 00:38:10,400
 Moo Hyul: Lee Do's bodyguard 

339
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:14,120
Actually, His Highness

340
00:38:15,760 --> 00:38:18,580
came with me.

341
00:38:18,580 --> 00:38:20,140
Pardon?

342
00:38:21,980 --> 00:38:24,260
He wants to meet you.

343
00:38:25,880 --> 00:38:30,400
He's waiting at the shore. Do you want to go?

344
00:38:40,040 --> 00:38:42,360
What did she say?

345
00:38:44,480 --> 00:38:46,220
About that...

346
00:38:48,700 --> 00:38:50,840
Is that so?

347
00:38:55,280 --> 00:38:59,900
 If I see Your Highness, I think it will be harder to go on. 

