00:39:10,060 --> 00:39:13,560
I heard you're the leader of this village.

350
00:39:16,920 --> 00:39:18,720
Yes.

351
00:39:24,380 --> 00:39:26,700
Why are you staring at me like that?

352
00:39:26,700 --> 00:39:30,620
 So you're his son. Still, how can you... 

