00:39:30,620 --> 00:39:36,180
 Prince Chung Nyeong, where are you? It's time go! 

354
00:39:37,620 --> 00:39:43,320
I have something to ask you but I have to go now.

355
00:39:43,320 --> 00:39:45,460
Your Highness.

