Is it okay... for me to hug Your Highness just once?

357
00:40:24,840 --> 00:40:27,670
I'm sorry.

358
00:40:28,750 --> 00:40:31,300
I

359
00:40:31,300 --> 00:40:35,310
just suddenly thought of my childhood.

360
00:40:37,970 --> 00:40:42,690
His Highness the King has been the same, right?

361
00:40:43,650 --> 00:40:50,420
Well, he's the same. He's lonely.

362
00:41:12,930 --> 00:41:15,250
 The Anbyeon Chaek 

363
00:41:16,270 --> 00:41:20,860
 has been approved! 

364
00:41:21,570 --> 00:41:23,600
 Give it here. 

365
00:41:25,040 --> 00:41:28,990
 You... I really love you. 

366
00:41:28,990 --> 00:41:31,510
 I won't be able to do anything 

