00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:51,030
 Boon Yi, you will be smiling somewhere else. 

370
00:41:51,920 --> 00:41:54,600
 For me to be able to think that way. 

371
00:42:29,910 --> 00:42:33,660
Leader, are you really going?

372
00:42:33,660 --> 00:42:36,370
I should go out once before my body becomes weaker.

373
00:42:36,420 --> 00:42:38,560
I don't even know if it will be the last.

374
00:42:38,580 --> 00:42:42,740
- The boat trip is too dangerous.
- The tides seem to be good.

375
00:42:42,780 --> 00:42:45,810
The Japanese pirates aren't around anymore either.

376
00:42:45,850 --> 00:42:47,500
Ah, you talk so much.

377
00:42:47,500 --> 00:42:50,780
You nag too much for a person going on a trip.

378
00:42:50,810 --> 00:42:54,850
I knew you'd be scolded. Let's go, Leader.

