00:45:01,320 --> 00:45:03,560
That's why, just like what Chae Yoon said,

404
00:45:03,590 --> 00:45:06,190
"If you don't learn this, you'll get boils!"

405
00:45:06,210 --> 00:45:10,730
- You should've warned them like that.
