406
00:45:10,750 --> 00:45:13,610
Do you think the children would study it because they're scared of boils?

407
00:45:13,610 --> 00:45:16,150
This piglet!

408
00:45:16,170 --> 00:45:18,800
You're starting again!

409
00:45:26,080 --> 00:45:30,860
Grandma, do you want to learn these letters?
 (Geun Ji) 

410
00:45:31,550 --> 00:45:35,450
When would I finish learning these letters at this age?

411
00:45:35,500 --> 00:45:39,880
They're really easy. Even a fool can learn it in ten days.

412
00:45:39,880 --> 00:45:41,400
A wise man can learn it in a day.

