00:45:41,400 --> 00:45:44,050
It took me three days.

414
00:45:44,100 --> 00:45:47,800
This piglet here probably took ten days. Right?

415
00:45:49,210 --> 00:45:52,190
I am someone who officially passed the military exam.

416
00:45:52,190 --> 00:45:55,640
A guy like you who came from the North, how dare you compare yourself to me?

417
00:45:55,660 --> 00:45:57,530
Stop fighting already!

418
00:45:58,730 --> 00:46:01,980
 Ten days? Within ten days? 

