00:46:14,560 --> 00:46:16,490
I have a friend called Chae Yoon.

424
00:46:16,540 --> 00:46:20,130
That guy didn't even take an afternoon to learn it all.

425
00:46:20,150 --> 00:46:23,640
- Right?
- Could it be...

426
00:46:24,170 --> 00:46:26,740
Can all the letters really

