00:47:42,750 --> 00:47:44,520
That's what I'm saying.

443
00:47:44,520 --> 00:47:46,970
While telling that guy to make such sounds,

444
00:47:46,970 --> 00:47:50,380
His Highness made those strange letters.

445
00:47:50,380 --> 00:47:52,920
No, I...

