00:54:46,980 --> 00:54:51,640
 You were all difficult people. 

514
00:54:51,640 --> 00:54:55,600
 You didn't oppose or fight me but... 

515
00:54:57,010 --> 00:55:00,030
 You didn't open your hearts entirely 

516
00:55:00,030 --> 00:55:03,110
 and didn't come into my hands, 

