00:55:34,280 --> 00:55:36,300
General Lee Jung Mo.

519
00:55:37,370 --> 00:55:39,090
Yes, Your Highness.

520
00:55:39,090 --> 00:55:43,290
Where is the base of the Japanese pirates in this area?

